"When Edmund de Tudenham was born about 1200, in Norfolk, England, United Kingdom, his father, John I Tudenham, was 31 and his mother, Tudenham, was 22. He married Gundreda Gundrilda Monasterin in 1240, in Norfolk, England. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died in 1248, at the age of 49."},"et":{"ABT 1200–1248":"umbes 1200–1248","1200–1248":"1200–1248","1204–1242":"1204–1242","1242–1292":"1242–1292","1171–Male":"1171–Surnud","1180–Female":"1180–Surnud","1248":"1248","1204":"1204","ABT 1200":"umbes 1200","1200":"1200","abt. 1242":"1242","1242":"1242","1240":"1240","1171":"1171","1292":"1292","1180":"1180","Oxburgh Hall, Oxborough, Norfolk, England":"Oxborough, Norfolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Church Stauton, Devon, England":"Devon, England","Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, England","Oxburg, Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"ABT 1200–1248":"noin 1200–1248","1200–1248":"1200–1248","1204–1242":"1204–1242","1242–1292":"1242–1292","1171–Male":"1171–Kuollut","1180–Female":"1180–Kuollut","1248":"1248","1204":"1204","ABT 1200":"noin 1200","1200":"1200","abt. 1242":"1242","1242":"1242","1240":"1240","1171":"1171","1292":"1292","1180":"1180","Oxburgh Hall, Oxborough, Norfolk, England":"Oxborough, Norfolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Church Stauton, Devon, England":"Devon, England","Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, England","Oxburg, Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"ABT 1200–1248":"environ 1200–1248","1200–1248":"1200–1248","1204–1242":"1204–1242","1242–1292":"1242–1292","1171–Male":"1171–Décédé","1180–Female":"1180–Décédée","1248":"1248","1204":"1204","ABT 1200":"environ 1200","1200":"1200","abt. 1242":"1242","1242":"1242","1240":"1240","1171":"1171","1292":"1292","1180":"1180","Oxburgh Hall, Oxborough, Norfolk, England":"Oxborough, Norfolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Church Stauton, Devon, England":"Devon, Angleterre","Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, Angleterre","Oxburg, Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, A